<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column">
      <div style="display: flex; border-bottom: solid 1px gray">
        <h1
          style="
            margin: 0;
            align-self: center;
            font-weight: bolder;
            font-size: 42px;
          "
        >
          Website
        </h1>
        <svg
          width="64px"
          height="64px"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          style="display: inline-block"
        >
          <g id="bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g>
          <g
            id="tracerCarrier"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          ></g>
          <g id="iconCarrier">
            <path
              d="M4 7.00005L10.2 11.65C11.2667 12.45 12.7333 12.45 13.8 11.65L20 7"
              stroke="#000000"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
            ></path>
            <rect
              x="3"
              y="5"
              width="18"
              height="14"
              rx="2"
              stroke="#000000"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
            ></rect>
          </g>
        </svg>
        <h2
          style="
            margin: 0;
            margin-right: 1rem;
            align-self: center;
            margin-left: 1rem;
          "
        >
          Активация аккаунта
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column">
        <p>Для активации аккаунта перейдите по ссылке ниже</p>
        <a
          href="https://{{ .URL }}"
          style="
            padding: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: rgb(248 250 252);
          "
          >https://{{ .URL }}</a
        >
        <p>С уважением, команда Website</p>
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: row;
          padding: 2rem;
          border-top: 1px solid gray;
          justify-content: center;
        "
      >
        <h3>2024 Copyright Наугольнов Артём</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
